    "Furthermore, reinforcement learning from human feedback (RLHF) is a process that requires the involvement of humans in ranking the output efficacy (human feedback) [7].",
    "The RLHF process was fundamental to the success of ChatGPT.",
    "Remarkably, each of the fine-tuning or RLHF steps can be executed either independently or sequentially.",
